<h1>Welcome</h1>

<p>You have one hour to complete as many tasks as you can. You might not finish all of them and that's okay.</p>
<ul>
<li>Sort names by First Name</li>
<li>Add additional people using API from https://randomuser.me/ everytime user clicks button below and person should be added without page refresh</li>
<li>Add delete icon (using Font Awesome) next to person and clicking it removes person from db</li>
<li>Update text on page to use Tahoma font</li>
<li>Make all photos look the same size at 200x200 (keeping aspect ratio)</li>
<li>Clean up page so photo on left and labels and data on the right of the photo (<a href="https://docs.google.com/presentation/d/1Ljdbw7Ea5Z3JAmpgK-mSjOJTmW2mGIGjnUqng53TN5I/edit?usp=sharing" target=_blank>see example)</a></li>
</ul>

<button>Add Person via API</button>
<hr/>
<% @everyone.each do |person| %>
  <label>
    Photo
    <div><img src='<%=person.photo_large %>'/></div>
  </label>
  <label>
    First Name
    <div><%=person.first %></div>
  </label>
  <label>
    Last Name
    <div><%=person.last %></div>
  </label>
  <label>
    City
    <div><%=person.city %></div>
  </label>
  <label>
    Cell Phone
    <div><%=person.cell %></div>
  </label>
<% end %>